kpi.name: M386B2C11

kpi_info.title: The longest call setup time of the failed call setup attempts
kpi_info.use: The longest call setup time from the failed call setup attempts, which terminated in the normal release (where the clear code is in the range of 001-3FF). The unit of time in ASCII report is seconds, in XML reports, it is 10 milliseconds.

kpi.kpi_alias: The longest call setup time of the failed call setup attempts
